yTime":"2018-06-23T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f6ddfaaad1806705f6a16965318eef4ea2616f","tid":713714,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9d0b8036ead650b1b6e34bfb2e11e2d93abc0f","tid":713714,"uid":123456,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以話<br />\n全部女人都係雞</span>"},{"pid":"6396c1531bd49ae228f22bec48650f0a93de18d2","tid":713714,"uid":121146,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線女人  澳門全部都係雞"},{"pid":"01f4eafc6647e8291aa055d6971685093ad5e2ab","tid":713714,"uid":187076,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/161624_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F161624_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=137c9bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37d965a1378714c9ec8126df41b64a01004f2dd2","tid":713714,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"越想越不對勁"},{"pid":"daad66f40595bc177da95acccf57032e84f7b0c5","tid":713714,"uid":48222,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"睇完篇文似係返到澳門比條仔發現偷食，返轉頭想屈錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0ba5524868b59769481a85b5b7605e95ce4cf3","tid":713714,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"澳門女啲身材普遍有睇頭過港女"},{"pid":"b20406ff80a868cbd5d0cf66e49571ed63dfa1c5","tid":713714,"uid":11962,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"或曰︰「台灣者，盪女痴男滿盈。其人好譏香港為支那，不然，則思淫亂。惑人妻、亂人夫，刁風月，弄牆隙、交合行淫，行淫交合，迷姦強暴，強暴迷姦，不絕於城也。堂姊、表妹、兄嫂、內娣、朋女、友孫、皆可慾淫。弱女信徒，秘書病人，或其親朋子侄，無一倖免。女盜口穴逢迎，奪夥計貞操。師者巨乳貶壓，誘學子心性。亦不然，交合時暗錄活春宮，分別時皇皇然脅之，又得幾回歡愉。女甫口角，輒奔舊愛，哭啼哭啼，又變嘿咻嘿咻。男欲內發，女言不可，搖頭嗔目，元陽閉穴。」此之謂也。"},{"pid":"d58a658f0a08a92665de0a366aacf27318aeddd7","tid":713714,"uid":14103,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔起訴就算？ 大佬 你插水都冇黃牌？"},{"pid":"a855ebda28ae633f8340540124072d572a61be96","tid":713714,"uid":11442,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"計咗咁耐分<br />\n有無個龍虎榜睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cccd112f71a18f985aefad67c8c01ecd8ffacd8","tid":713714,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a855ebda28ae633f8340540124072d572a61be96","tid":713714,"uid":11442,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"計咗咁耐分<br />\n有無個龍虎榜睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇<br />\n<br />\n新北市跑贏大市"},{"pid":"04a8e3fd8f0967b6f79ef8f23b2e27c5b84719de","tid":713714,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cccd112f71a18f985aefad67c8c01ecd8ffacd8","tid":713714,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a855ebda28ae633f8340540124072d572a61be96","tid":713714,"uid":11442,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"計咗咁耐分<br />\n有無個龍虎榜睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇<br />\n<br />\n新北市跑贏大市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"新北市就好似德甲入面拜仁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid